    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Banská Štiavnica Town Council (Bratislava, 1
                    December 1548)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>The letter is about a physician called Ioannes, Oláh asks not to give up
                            their previous benevolence towards the physician.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Prudentes et Circumspecti Domini et Amici nobis Honorandi, salutem!</p>
                <p>Intelleximus vos anno superiore Deo <gap extent="1" reason="illegible"
                        unit="word"/>
                    <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/> con<gap extent="unknown"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> vestro pro commodiori <gap extent="1"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> non sui ex vestro erga eum favore et
                    benevolentia <gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>larii
                        liberta<gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/> commode <gap
                        extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>s<gap extent="unknown"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> concessisse. Quid <gap extent="1"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> magno a vobis beneficio afflictum palam <choice>
                        <orig>peren<gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied>peren<corr>nem</corr></supplied>
                    </choice>
                    <gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>m<gap extent="unknown"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> dictum ista vos publice interdixisse, ne
                    quid <gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>ruis<gap
                        extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/> amplius <gap extent="1"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> sed tamen ex hordeo coqueret. Propter quod
                        <persName>Ioannes doctor</persName><note type="critic">We do not know him
                        more closely.</note> non mediocriter et turbatus nequaquam <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>ne</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>ordi</corr>ne</supplied>
                    </choice> vitae augeretur postquam liberius coquendi triticeae <gap extent="1"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> per vos sibi sublata esset p<gap
                        extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>inde ne idem
                        <persName>Ioannes doctor</persName> pristinam erga se benevolentiam reliqua
                    ulla ex parte diminutam esse sentiat, cumquam <gap extent="unknown"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/>ntunde vitae <gap extent="1"
                        reason="illegible" unit="word"/> sit <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>rigatum</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>cor</corr>rigatum</supplied>
                    </choice>. Rogamus Vos velint <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>
                    <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/> causam reliquam pristino vestro
                    favore amplecti <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>
                    <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/> eo quo ante iure ei re<gap
                        extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>
                    <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="word"/>ciei</orig>
                        <supplied><corr>perni</corr>ciei</supplied>
                    </choice>rependemus, vosque bene <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied><corr>valere optamus</corr></supplied>
                    </choice>. </p>
                <p>Datum <placeName>Posonii</placeName> prima die Decembris <choice>
                        <orig><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="word"/></orig>
                        <supplied><corr>anno Domini</corr></supplied>
                    </choice> 1548.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Zagrabiensis
                            secretarius cancellarius regiae maiestatis etc. manu propria</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p>Prudentibus et circumspectis dominis iudici et iuratis civibus
                    civitatis Semniciensis etc. amicis nobis honorandis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
